name: Pressure
description:
Inktober prompt day 9: Pressure
Made with physical collage using vintage magazine ads from Nat Geo and an ad book, drawing using micron pens, and Photoshop textured brushes. This is about the pressures from society to be a woman. Feeling like we have to smile, be graceful, wear bras, be and act a certain way, etc. This is the deepest piece I've made for Inktober so far.
